WEBVTT

00:00.140 --> 00:01.746
_

00:01.772 --> 00:04.210
- I'd like us to stay friends.
- Yeah, I'd like that.

00:04.735 --> 00:06.914
Would you like to go
for a drink sometime?

00:06.939 --> 00:08.000
Sure, yeah.

00:08.026 --> 00:09.856
- I had a really good night.
- Me, too.

00:09.882 --> 00:11.494
I didn't want to sleep with him.

00:11.520 --> 00:13.862
We're from the Sexual
Offences Investigation Team.

00:13.888 --> 00:15.047
And I'm arresting you for rape.

00:15.073 --> 00:18.334
If I thought she didn't want to
sleep with me, I'd not have done it.

00:18.360 --> 00:20.519
- I said no!
- No, you didn't.

00:20.545 --> 00:22.665
- I love you, Katy.
- Stop, she's my little sister.

00:22.691 --> 00:25.174
We're a mistake, Tom. I can't do this.

00:25.200 --> 00:28.268
<i>Every colleague, every friend,
every member of his family.</i>

00:28.294 --> 00:29.494
Now they know.

00:31.000 --> 00:37.074
